WEBVTT

00:18.600 --> 00:19.600
Good stuff.

00:23.830 --> 00:24.600
Lord Cheng,

00:24.960 --> 00:26.550
what would you like to buy today?

00:26.550 --> 00:27.960
I just got a new batch of saddles.

00:27.960 --> 00:29.290
Shall I show them to you?

00:30.440 --> 00:32.100
What were you just looking at?

00:33.520 --> 00:34.030
Well...

00:39.240 --> 00:40.300
Nothing. Nothing.

00:40.600 --> 00:42.200
They are just ordinary ores.

00:42.470 --> 00:43.520
Nothing special.

00:43.750 --> 00:44.430
Lord Cheng,

00:44.430 --> 00:46.030
take a look at these saddles.

00:46.470 --> 00:47.530
They just arrived.

00:47.770 --> 00:48.900
How do you like them?

00:49.710 --> 00:50.790
They are all genuine leather.

00:50.790 --> 00:51.390
Look.

00:52.630 --> 00:54.240
Look, they are all new goods.

00:57.640 --> 00:58.440
Your Majesty.

00:59.320 --> 01:00.790
Due to tax reductions and exemptions,

01:00.790 --> 01:04.069
the army's supplies and soldiers' pay
have become insufficient.

01:04.069 --> 01:06.200
In addition, as the weather turns colder,

01:06.200 --> 01:08.789
we also need to prepare funds
for winter heating.

01:08.789 --> 01:09.850
If this continues,

01:10.150 --> 01:11.680
I'm afraid not only people,

01:12.200 --> 01:15.200
but also cattle and horses
may not survive the winter.

01:21.350 --> 01:22.840
Times are tough right now.

01:24.400 --> 01:26.640
Halve the cost of charcoal for heating.

01:27.510 --> 01:29.110
After surviving the winter,

01:29.280 --> 01:31.580
we'll have the soldiers
farm and herd in spring

01:31.580 --> 01:33.780
to increase grain and fodder supplies.

01:41.870 --> 01:42.670
Your Majesty.

01:54.870 --> 01:55.600
What is this?

01:56.479 --> 01:59.430
This kind of ore is currently circulating
in the markets of Great Yan.

01:59.430 --> 02:01.480
The common people
are using it as a form of currency.

02:01.480 --> 02:03.810
I heard Ximeng has discovered black gold.

02:04.310 --> 02:06.370
I didn't expect
that it has reached Great Yan.

02:06.370 --> 02:08.530
It seems the output is astonishing.

02:08.710 --> 02:11.570
Moreover, Ximeng has risen rapidly
in recent times

02:11.580 --> 02:12.970
and introduced many new policies.

02:12.970 --> 02:13.560
I suspect

02:14.120 --> 02:15.920
it is related to this black gold.

03:38.420 --> 03:43.829
[REBIRTH]

03:44.300 --> 03:46.820
[Episode 29]

03:49.030 --> 03:49.829
Young Master,

03:50.000 --> 03:51.150
over the past few days,
there have indeed been

03:51.150 --> 03:53.750
some people from Great Yong in Ximengcheng
whose movements are suspicious.

03:53.750 --> 03:55.030
Lord Zhuge said in his letter

03:55.030 --> 03:57.079
that he will arrive in Ximengcheng
in 3 days to meet you.

03:57.079 --> 03:58.280
Is it possible

03:58.510 --> 04:01.910
that people from Qingshan Manor
are already in Ximengcheng?

04:02.280 --> 04:03.870
Qingshan Manor inherently carries out

04:03.870 --> 04:06.150
assassinations and investigations
for the royal family.

04:06.150 --> 04:08.710
They have strongholds
in both Great Yan and Biantang.

04:08.710 --> 04:10.470
Since my grandfather could find me here

04:10.470 --> 04:11.870
and send a secret letter,

04:11.910 --> 04:13.400
it means in Ximengcheng,

04:13.710 --> 04:15.680
there must be strongholds
of Qingshan Manor.

04:15.680 --> 04:16.430
Young Master,

04:16.430 --> 04:17.380
then what should we...

04:17.380 --> 04:18.220
Don't worry.

04:18.510 --> 04:20.269
Since grandfather is coming to see me,

04:20.269 --> 04:22.240
he'll make sure I can find him.

05:00.070 --> 05:00.870
Young Master.

05:05.000 --> 05:06.400
I hope you have been well.

05:08.830 --> 05:09.690
I did not expect

05:10.430 --> 05:12.690
that even Ximeng, a land without a ruler,

05:13.000 --> 05:15.390
is still within the reach
of Qingshan Manor's eyes and ears.

05:15.390 --> 05:18.190
There's much you don't know.

05:24.320 --> 05:27.430
[Zhuge Muqing, Chief of Qingshan Manor]

05:30.680 --> 05:31.480
Grandfather?

05:32.270 --> 05:34.600
I just lost my ability
to use martial arts.

05:35.070 --> 05:37.430
I won't die anytime soon.

05:38.190 --> 05:38.950
Why?

05:40.240 --> 05:41.570
What exactly happened?

05:41.680 --> 05:42.730
It was His Majesty.

05:42.730 --> 05:44.120
[Zhan Fu, Spy of Qingshan Manor]

05:42.930 --> 05:44.060
He forced the Master

05:44.680 --> 05:47.540
to take poison
that destroyed all his martial arts.

05:51.830 --> 05:52.960
It was because of me?

05:53.390 --> 05:54.000
Yes,

05:54.680 --> 05:55.600
and no.

05:56.240 --> 05:57.940
The Emperor relies heavily
on Qingshan Manor,

05:57.940 --> 05:59.500
but he also fears it.

05:59.530 --> 06:01.000
With the defeat at Meilin Pass,

06:01.000 --> 06:03.830
he blamed our Zhuge family.

06:04.560 --> 06:06.360
Do you think that clumsy corpse

06:06.360 --> 06:07.870
could fool Yan Xun

06:07.870 --> 06:09.870
and Qingshan Manor?

06:09.870 --> 06:12.000
You couldn't even fool Qingshan Manor.

06:12.000 --> 06:13.310
How could you fool the Muhe family,

06:13.310 --> 06:14.430
or those wolves and tigers

06:14.430 --> 06:17.510
waiting to tear our Zhuge family apart?

06:17.680 --> 06:19.360
To avoid revealing any flaws,

06:19.510 --> 06:21.270
we whipped the corpse

06:21.510 --> 06:23.270
and threw it into a mass grave

06:23.830 --> 06:25.620
to be torn apart by wild wolves.

06:25.750 --> 06:26.870
But even so,

06:28.190 --> 06:30.450
His Majesty wouldn't easily believe it.

06:30.600 --> 06:33.390
So you had to use the excuse
of apologizing

06:33.800 --> 06:35.460
and destroy your martial arts

06:35.830 --> 06:37.480
to quell his suspicions.

06:38.270 --> 06:39.630
Not only that.

06:40.750 --> 06:42.360
The Muhe family advised His Majesty

06:42.360 --> 06:44.510
that it was your infiltration
into Great Yan

06:44.510 --> 06:47.630
that alerted the enemy
and delayed the military operation,

06:47.630 --> 06:49.890
causing the great defeat at Meilin Pass.

06:50.630 --> 06:52.560
Half of the spies of Qingshan Manor

06:53.120 --> 06:55.190
were executed.

07:01.390 --> 07:02.190
Grandfather.

07:04.240 --> 07:05.190
It was my fault.

07:05.630 --> 07:06.240
No.

07:07.310 --> 07:08.870
It was the Muhe family.

07:10.240 --> 07:11.830
They have long been trying to replace

07:11.830 --> 07:13.390
Qingshan Manor.

07:13.830 --> 07:16.270
The defeat at Meilin Pass
was just an excuse.

07:16.270 --> 07:17.190
So, Yue,

07:17.560 --> 07:18.750
that's why

07:19.870 --> 07:22.240
I came to Ximeng in person
to take you back.

07:23.040 --> 07:26.480
You are now King Ximeng.

07:27.000 --> 07:29.950
By submitting to Great Yong
under this identity,

07:30.720 --> 07:32.360
you will become a great asset

07:32.360 --> 07:33.750
to our Zhuge family.

07:34.240 --> 07:36.240
The Muhe family's wishful thinking

07:37.120 --> 07:38.560
will come to nothing.

08:02.240 --> 08:03.040
Grandfather.

08:03.160 --> 08:03.830
Yue.

08:04.750 --> 08:05.800
I have failed you.

08:06.980 --> 08:08.710
I have failed your upbringing.

08:09.040 --> 08:10.170
But I've decided...

08:11.040 --> 08:12.440
to leave Qingshan Manor.

08:13.680 --> 08:15.010
Please forget about me.

08:16.930 --> 08:18.390
Just pretend I really died

08:20.160 --> 08:21.510
in the frozen lake.

08:22.510 --> 08:23.120
Yue,

08:24.750 --> 08:26.610
can you really give up everything

08:27.770 --> 08:29.980
and leave with that slave girl?

08:30.600 --> 08:32.000
Where can you go and hide?

08:32.789 --> 08:33.870
In Ximeng?

08:35.030 --> 08:37.000
Or at the ends of the earth?

08:37.510 --> 08:39.169
Qingshan Manor and Great Yong

08:39.610 --> 08:41.570
will find you eventually.

08:50.550 --> 08:51.200
Yue.

08:55.000 --> 08:56.240
You can find me,

08:57.510 --> 08:58.790
but you can't take me away.

08:58.790 --> 08:59.630
This...

09:00.840 --> 09:03.200
is the grandson I raised since childhood.

09:03.560 --> 09:04.830
Now you have

09:06.230 --> 09:08.320
the power to threaten me.

09:11.390 --> 09:12.720
But does that Chu Qiao

09:13.190 --> 09:14.790
know who personally

09:15.550 --> 09:17.390
sent Yan Shicheng's family

09:18.000 --> 09:19.720
to Jiuyou Platform back then?

09:20.910 --> 09:21.600
Back then,

09:22.790 --> 09:24.150
I had no choice.

09:25.030 --> 09:26.240
Even if she knows,

09:27.870 --> 09:29.030
she will forgive me.

09:29.510 --> 09:30.320
Even if

09:30.910 --> 09:33.240
you can explain the Yan Shicheng case,

09:34.750 --> 09:35.480
can you

09:36.480 --> 09:38.630
explain all the dirty deeds

09:39.080 --> 09:41.000
committed by Qingshan Manor?

09:41.280 --> 09:43.870
Qingshan Manor works for His Majesty.

09:43.890 --> 09:45.850
How many people have we massacred?

09:47.840 --> 09:49.960
Although you didn't kill them yourself,

09:49.960 --> 09:51.960
you are the Chief of Qingshan Manor.

09:52.870 --> 09:55.080
Can you absolve yourself?

09:58.240 --> 09:58.840
Yue,

10:00.390 --> 10:02.590
once you are a member of Qingshan Manor,

10:04.270 --> 10:05.790
you always will be.

10:11.790 --> 10:13.440
I am like this,

10:15.550 --> 10:17.270
and so are you.

10:19.790 --> 10:20.600
This...

10:22.910 --> 10:23.910
is our fate.

10:55.480 --> 10:56.410
What are these?

10:58.030 --> 10:59.750
Didn't we spread the word earlier

10:59.750 --> 11:01.510
that the Queen
loved crabapples and sand dates,

11:01.510 --> 11:03.000
and that King Ximeng
would pay a high price for them?

11:03.000 --> 11:03.910
This led everyone

11:03.910 --> 11:05.030
to plant them.

11:05.150 --> 11:06.630
The people who planted these fruits

11:06.630 --> 11:09.360
have rushed to deliver them
to the palace for you.

11:12.550 --> 11:14.960
That's because Ximeng's climate

11:15.120 --> 11:17.320
is suitable for planting these fruits.

11:18.790 --> 11:19.750
And what is this?

11:28.720 --> 11:29.910
This is a gift from the people of Ximeng

11:29.910 --> 11:32.600
to King Ximeng and Queen Ximeng.

11:32.790 --> 11:33.630
They say

11:33.660 --> 11:36.920
King Ximeng, without his mask,
is exceptionally handsome

11:37.240 --> 11:39.480
and a perfect match

11:39.670 --> 11:41.070
for the beautiful Queen.

11:43.630 --> 11:44.510
I think

11:44.960 --> 11:45.750
Ximeng's...

11:57.830 --> 11:58.400
Stop!

11:59.120 --> 12:00.270
This is King Ximeng's Palace!

12:00.270 --> 12:02.130
No entering without permission!

12:07.480 --> 12:09.880
I am the sister of Queen Ximeng.

12:13.970 --> 12:16.510
[Jing Xiaoba]

12:17.270 --> 12:17.910
My Lord.

12:19.240 --> 12:20.960
A woman outside is asking for an audience.

12:20.960 --> 12:22.320
She was stopped by the guards.

12:22.320 --> 12:24.120
She says she is the Queen's sister,

12:24.120 --> 12:25.580
whose name is Jing Xiaoba.

12:25.910 --> 12:27.720
Say that again. What is her name?

12:29.080 --> 12:30.080
Xiaoba...

12:30.320 --> 12:32.550
Jing... Xiaoba?

12:46.960 --> 12:47.600
Xiaoba!

13:09.600 --> 13:12.440
Qing...

13:12.440 --> 13:13.550
She seems to have stopped breathing.

13:13.550 --> 13:14.080
Qing?

13:14.540 --> 13:15.240
What's wrong with you?

13:15.240 --> 13:16.510
Qing is dead.

13:24.480 --> 13:25.080
Sixth Sister!

13:25.080 --> 13:25.750
Xiaoba!

13:27.200 --> 13:28.630
What are you all waiting for?

13:28.630 --> 13:29.320
Let's go!

13:29.960 --> 13:30.600
Hurry!

13:30.790 --> 13:31.510
Go!

13:32.360 --> 13:33.160
Sixth Sister,

13:33.600 --> 13:34.790
Qing is...

13:36.440 --> 13:37.000
Go!

13:38.360 --> 13:39.550
Hurry, keep up!

13:44.270 --> 13:44.910
Xiaoba!

13:46.670 --> 13:47.440
Get down!

13:51.200 --> 13:52.670
Hurry! Don't let them escape!

13:52.670 --> 13:53.240
Run!

14:02.480 --> 14:03.480
Well, well, well.

14:03.790 --> 14:06.250
You lowly slaves
are really tired of living.

14:07.080 --> 14:08.960
Take them back
and cripple their hands and feet.

14:08.960 --> 14:12.320
Serving the Old Master
doesn't require hands and feet anyway.

14:12.320 --> 14:13.120
Take them down!

14:13.120 --> 14:13.750
Yes!

14:24.250 --> 14:25.510
You really are Xiaoba.

14:41.920 --> 14:43.520
Ever since we got separated,

14:44.360 --> 14:46.420
I've been sending people to find you.

14:46.550 --> 14:47.880
I finally see you today.

14:48.840 --> 14:50.040
It's just wonderful.

14:51.390 --> 14:52.190
Sixth Sister.

14:53.630 --> 14:54.600
Long time no see.

14:56.550 --> 14:57.510
Long time no see.

14:58.420 --> 14:59.900
It's so good to see you.

15:00.360 --> 15:00.960
Let's go.

15:01.320 --> 15:02.980
I'll take you into the palace.

15:12.320 --> 15:12.750
Xiaoba.

15:12.750 --> 15:13.440
Your Majesty.

15:13.440 --> 15:14.870
You must be tired

15:14.870 --> 15:15.720
after traveling so far to get here.

15:15.720 --> 15:17.200
Take a hot bath later

15:17.280 --> 15:19.010
and change into clean clothes.

15:19.710 --> 15:20.280
Let's go.

15:24.150 --> 15:25.120
Who is this?

15:51.510 --> 15:53.030
This is the first time

15:53.440 --> 15:55.700
I've seen such a luxurious bathing pool.

15:55.960 --> 15:56.760
Sixth Sister,

15:57.510 --> 15:59.240
you are living such a good life.

15:59.720 --> 16:00.630
Unlike me,

16:01.550 --> 16:03.510
who is as poor as a beggar.

16:05.870 --> 16:09.360
I was separated from you
when I fled from Great Yong to Great Yan.

16:09.360 --> 16:11.320
After I settled down in Great Yan,

16:11.320 --> 16:12.720
I sent people to find you.

16:12.870 --> 16:13.930
But unexpectedly,

16:14.200 --> 16:15.750
before you returned,

16:15.870 --> 16:16.960
I had an accident

16:17.150 --> 16:18.680
and fell into a frozen lake.

16:19.360 --> 16:20.080
I know.

16:21.230 --> 16:24.160
The Universal Harmony Guild
brought me to Great Yan.

16:25.030 --> 16:26.630
Miss Zhong once took me in.

16:27.750 --> 16:29.680
Later, something happened to her,

16:30.870 --> 16:32.530
leaving me with nowhere to go.

16:32.960 --> 16:34.960
I could only wander around Great Yan

16:35.240 --> 16:36.630
in disguise.

16:37.550 --> 16:38.200
Xiaoba,

16:39.790 --> 16:41.390
you must have suffered a lot.

16:43.320 --> 16:44.720
After I went to Biantang,

16:45.080 --> 16:47.010
I had Minglu keep asking about you,

16:47.150 --> 16:49.350
but we couldn't find your whereabouts.

16:49.390 --> 16:51.390
Great Yan has been constantly at war

16:51.550 --> 16:52.720
and in chaos.

16:53.670 --> 16:54.870
You were in Biantang,

16:55.550 --> 16:57.480
so naturally you couldn't find me.

16:57.910 --> 16:58.710
Fortunately,

16:59.080 --> 17:00.740
we sisters finally reunited.

17:01.150 --> 17:03.210
This is truly a blessing from Heaven.

17:25.589 --> 17:27.510
My beautiful sister is back.

17:28.440 --> 17:29.640
These are my clothes.

17:29.780 --> 17:32.020
I will prepare new ones for you later.

17:35.680 --> 17:36.480
Sixth Sister,

17:36.960 --> 17:38.070
I'm a little hungry.

17:38.070 --> 17:39.590
Can you get me some food?

17:40.510 --> 17:41.070
Okay.

17:41.440 --> 17:42.770
I will go arrange it now.

18:08.000 --> 18:08.640
Xing.

18:23.000 --> 18:23.750
Guards!

18:24.200 --> 18:25.000
Help!

18:25.070 --> 18:25.960
Help!

18:29.160 --> 18:30.160
Sixth Sister!

18:31.640 --> 18:32.430
Sixth Sister!

18:32.430 --> 18:34.300
-Zhuge Yue wanted to harass me.
-Xiaoba!

18:34.300 --> 18:35.740
Kill him for me!

18:41.720 --> 18:43.830
Zhuge Yue shouldn't be
such a despicable person.

18:43.830 --> 18:45.200
Why are you doing this?

18:48.640 --> 18:49.830
I hate him.

18:54.790 --> 18:55.920
I want him dead!

18:56.920 --> 18:57.830
Eldest Sister,

18:58.550 --> 18:59.480
Fifth Brother—

19:00.500 --> 19:01.960
all my family

19:02.500 --> 19:04.260
died in Qingshan Manor.

19:04.920 --> 19:07.110
Why can Zhuge Yue live so well?

19:07.720 --> 19:08.750
Why?

19:10.160 --> 19:10.790
Xiaoba,

19:11.550 --> 19:13.480
Zhuge Yue has left Qingshan Manor.

19:13.750 --> 19:14.920
But the Qingshan Manor under his command

19:14.920 --> 19:16.680
killed all my family.

19:17.840 --> 19:19.160
Can simply leaving

19:19.200 --> 19:21.960
wipe off all the blood debts?

19:22.030 --> 19:22.800
Xiaoba!

19:23.310 --> 19:24.240
Let me explain.

19:24.830 --> 19:27.000
Brother Linxi's death
was a misunderstanding.

19:27.000 --> 19:28.290
Zhuge Yue had no choice.

19:28.290 --> 19:29.130
Jing Xiaoliu!

19:29.680 --> 19:31.920
How did Brother Linxi treat you back then?

19:31.920 --> 19:33.350
If you really see us as family,

19:33.350 --> 19:34.790
you should kill Zhuge Yue

19:34.790 --> 19:36.400
to avenge Linxi, who's dead!

19:36.480 --> 19:37.640
Why can't you do it?

19:43.880 --> 19:45.740
Because you are not Jing Xiaoliu.

19:46.310 --> 19:47.440
You are Chu Qiao,

19:48.240 --> 19:49.640
Queen Ximeng.

19:53.680 --> 19:55.640
You are not my real sister.

19:56.550 --> 19:57.960
My real sister

19:59.030 --> 20:00.960
already died in Qingshan Manor.

20:02.240 --> 20:05.830
All of my family died in Qingshan Manor.

20:13.880 --> 20:15.030
I came here this time

20:16.480 --> 20:18.030
just to use you

20:19.070 --> 20:20.680
to get close to Zhuge Yue

20:22.270 --> 20:24.350
and avenge my family.

20:25.270 --> 20:26.550
Since I've failed,

20:27.400 --> 20:28.930
it doesn't matter anymore.

20:34.110 --> 20:35.440
Just kill me.

20:36.830 --> 20:38.240
That way, our Jing family

20:39.590 --> 20:42.070
can reunite in the underworld.

20:54.550 --> 20:55.200
Xiaoba,

20:55.960 --> 20:57.780
if you don't want to accept me
as your sister,

20:57.780 --> 20:58.950
I won't force you.

21:04.680 --> 21:05.540
Take this horse

21:06.240 --> 21:07.000
with you.

21:08.090 --> 21:09.350
There is a bundle on it,

21:09.920 --> 21:12.120
which contains some rations and money.

21:12.400 --> 21:14.000
If you encounter any difficulties
in the future,

21:14.000 --> 21:15.600
you can come find me anytime.

22:15.550 --> 22:18.200
I got this scar
while attacking Li'ancheng.

22:18.880 --> 22:20.480
It has already scabbed over.

22:20.550 --> 22:22.210
No need for medicine anymore.

22:30.270 --> 22:31.550
This scar is the same.

22:32.190 --> 22:33.790
It has healed a long time ago.

22:38.680 --> 22:40.920
Then shouldn't the wound
you got at Qingshan Manor

22:40.920 --> 22:42.400
be healed by now?

22:47.320 --> 22:48.270
Let bygones

22:49.070 --> 22:50.200
be bygones.

24:25.000 --> 24:26.400
Why are you following me?

24:31.240 --> 24:32.570
You regret letting me go

24:32.640 --> 24:34.300
and want to kill me now, right?

24:35.720 --> 24:36.980
The dagger in your hand

24:37.920 --> 24:40.780
is made of glazed iron
exclusive to Qingshan Manor.

24:41.880 --> 24:43.830
Its poison is lethal upon drawing blood.

24:43.830 --> 24:44.400
I...

24:45.160 --> 24:48.020
I didn't know
this was a dagger from Qingshan Manor.

24:49.720 --> 24:50.880
Can you tell me

24:52.440 --> 24:53.750
who gave it to you?

24:55.240 --> 24:56.070
Before,

24:56.830 --> 24:58.090
I was wandering around

24:58.720 --> 25:00.320
and almost starved to death.

25:01.030 --> 25:02.790
A masked swordsman saved me.

25:03.160 --> 25:04.880
He told me he was also a slave,

25:05.200 --> 25:07.640
and his family
was killed by Qingshan Manor as well,

25:07.640 --> 25:10.790
so he helped me find you for revenge.

25:24.310 --> 25:25.110
Grandfather?

25:27.070 --> 25:27.830
Yue,

25:28.400 --> 25:31.070
I knew you would find out
and follow her here.

25:31.200 --> 25:31.960
Yes.

25:32.300 --> 25:35.700
I was the one who arranged for Jing Xiaoba
to assassinate you.

25:37.030 --> 25:37.960
It was you?

25:41.070 --> 25:42.240
You used me?

25:43.270 --> 25:44.400
I will kill you!

25:48.160 --> 25:50.200
If you want to save this girl,

25:51.550 --> 25:53.550
come back to Qingshan Manor with me.

25:55.790 --> 25:56.990
She wanted to kill me,

25:57.830 --> 26:00.090
and you're using her life to threaten me?

26:00.440 --> 26:01.640
Isn't it ridiculous?

26:01.750 --> 26:03.240
She is Chu Qiao's sister.

26:03.350 --> 26:04.510
If she loses her life

26:05.130 --> 26:06.330
because of you,

26:06.360 --> 26:08.200
will Chu Qiao forgive you?

26:08.220 --> 26:10.150
I recognized this dagger long ago.

26:11.070 --> 26:12.800
But before I followed her here,

26:12.830 --> 26:14.230
I still held onto the hope

26:15.000 --> 26:16.590
that it wasn't you.

26:17.070 --> 26:17.930
I didn't expect

26:19.790 --> 26:21.070
I was too naive.

26:21.680 --> 26:23.000
I'm using this girl

26:23.720 --> 26:25.000
just to remind you

26:25.400 --> 26:27.660
that you are the Chief of Qingshan Manor.

26:28.200 --> 26:30.600
You can never wash the blood
off your hands.

26:31.010 --> 26:32.830
Jing Xiaoba is not the only means I have.

26:32.830 --> 26:34.310
I have other ways

26:34.400 --> 26:35.880
to uncover the past

26:36.380 --> 26:38.250
and make Chu Qiao see clearly

26:38.510 --> 26:39.960
what you have done

26:39.960 --> 26:41.290
and what Qingshan Manor

26:42.030 --> 26:43.480
has done before.

26:43.960 --> 26:45.960
Why do you have to force me like this?

26:48.350 --> 26:49.110
Yue,

26:50.070 --> 26:52.330
among the 3 branches of the Zhuge family,

26:52.640 --> 26:55.350
you are the only one I carefully raised.

26:55.550 --> 26:57.790
You are the only hope for Qingshan Manor

26:57.960 --> 27:00.350
and the Zhuge family to survive.

27:01.030 --> 27:03.200
I won't let you leave Qingshan Manor.

27:03.200 --> 27:04.000
Grandfather,

27:05.550 --> 27:06.310
am I...

27:07.070 --> 27:09.440
just a piece of your work?

27:10.680 --> 27:12.010
You should know clearly

27:12.960 --> 27:15.200
that once you are a member
of Qingshan Manor,

27:15.200 --> 27:17.240
you can never leave Qingshan Manor.

27:17.350 --> 27:18.350
Not just you,

27:18.790 --> 27:19.750
but also me,

27:20.070 --> 27:22.160
and every spy in Qingshan Manor.

27:22.160 --> 27:23.690
It is the same for everyone.

27:24.960 --> 27:26.880
I can give you 5 days.

27:27.440 --> 27:28.370
Five days later,

27:28.510 --> 27:31.490
I will be waiting for you
at the teahouse with Jing Xiaoba.

27:31.490 --> 27:32.690
What if I don't go?

27:33.000 --> 27:34.640
If you insist on having your own way,

27:34.640 --> 27:36.840
not only will Jing Xiaoba lose her life—

27:37.480 --> 27:38.880
you should know the rules.

27:38.880 --> 27:41.810
Qingshan Manor will definitely appoint
a new Chief.

27:41.850 --> 27:43.480
If this Chief is not you,

27:43.880 --> 27:47.030
your loyal Moon Guards
will all be executed,

27:47.440 --> 27:49.300
and their families will also die.

27:49.640 --> 27:52.750
They are all people
who have risked their lives for you.

27:53.310 --> 27:54.680
Can you really bear

27:54.680 --> 27:56.750
to watch them getting killed

27:58.400 --> 28:00.310
one by one?

28:10.000 --> 28:11.460
Broad beans, have a taste.

28:12.640 --> 28:14.000
Please come in, sir.

28:15.070 --> 28:15.640
Sir!

28:16.590 --> 28:17.250
A pot of tea.

28:17.830 --> 28:18.640
Coming.

28:21.000 --> 28:21.800
Young Master,

28:22.270 --> 28:24.600
this is the news we brought from Biantang.

28:25.110 --> 28:26.770
Sir, your business is not bad.

28:27.440 --> 28:29.680
It's mainly because the new policy
is so good.

28:29.680 --> 28:31.920
In the past, there was always
catching and killing,

28:29.930 --> 28:30.990
[Your Majesty, Chu Qiao is no longer
in Biantang territory.]

28:30.990 --> 28:32.050
[We have confirmed that she is now
in Ximeng with Zhuge Yue.]

28:32.000 --> 28:33.240
which made people panic.

28:33.240 --> 28:34.960
Business around here wasn't easy.

28:34.960 --> 28:37.760
You must have made a fortune
these past few months.

28:37.950 --> 28:39.000
I've been lucky.

28:39.030 --> 28:41.720
Not only are there merchant caravans
coming to Ximeng for business,

28:41.720 --> 28:43.830
but many people
from Great Yong and Great Yan

28:43.830 --> 28:46.030
have also moved here with them.

28:46.030 --> 28:47.070
Your business

28:47.070 --> 28:48.480
will definitely keep booming.

28:48.480 --> 28:49.880
Thank you. I sure hope so.

28:50.590 --> 28:51.270
Enjoy.

28:53.870 --> 28:54.590
Here, sir.

28:54.640 --> 28:55.770
Your tea and snacks.

28:58.590 --> 28:59.310
Sir,

28:59.400 --> 29:01.330
you are from Great Yan, aren't you?

29:04.110 --> 29:04.790
Yes.

29:05.550 --> 29:07.070
We are merchants from Great Yan.

29:07.070 --> 29:08.470
We want to buy some herbs.

29:08.750 --> 29:09.440
Sir,

29:10.150 --> 29:11.300
how did you know?

29:11.790 --> 29:13.600
My stall might be small,

29:13.640 --> 29:14.830
but ever since our King Ximeng

29:14.830 --> 29:16.830
issued the trade decree,

29:16.830 --> 29:19.400
I've seen plenty of merchant caravans.

29:19.720 --> 29:21.350
From your clothes and accent,

29:21.350 --> 29:22.880
I could guess roughly.

29:27.310 --> 29:28.000
Sir,

29:28.440 --> 29:29.770
you dropped something.

29:31.510 --> 29:32.110
Thank you.

29:34.350 --> 29:35.030
Sir,

29:35.350 --> 29:38.000
the woman in this portrait
is very beautiful.

29:38.230 --> 29:39.890
She looks a bit like our Queen.

29:42.590 --> 29:44.050
The woman in this portrait

29:45.960 --> 29:47.310
is the one I love.

29:49.030 --> 29:50.720
You are a lucky man, sir.

29:51.000 --> 29:52.080
Enjoy.

30:22.860 --> 30:23.580
Be careful.

30:24.170 --> 30:25.630
Thank you, General Cheng.

30:41.600 --> 30:42.270
Honey,

30:42.400 --> 30:44.330
I brought some fruit for you to try.

30:45.030 --> 30:46.290
You are so thoughtful.

30:47.510 --> 30:50.030
These are fresh apricots
and Xiangsuguo fruit.

30:50.030 --> 30:51.310
I picked them out especially.

30:51.310 --> 30:52.440
They are very sweet.

31:03.310 --> 31:04.370
Thank you, my dear.

31:09.000 --> 31:11.530
She doesn't look like
the one in the portrait.

31:18.640 --> 31:20.160
Here are the spy leaders

31:20.160 --> 31:22.440
of Qingshan Manor's 4 strongholds
in Ximeng.

31:22.440 --> 31:23.440
They're all here.

31:26.270 --> 31:27.200
I know

31:27.720 --> 31:29.030
you want to use them

31:29.240 --> 31:31.900
in exchange
for your freedom and Jing Xiaoba's.

31:32.070 --> 31:34.270
But you've overestimated their value.

31:34.440 --> 31:36.920
Qingshan Manor lacks anything but spies.

31:37.200 --> 31:38.270
A few deaths

31:39.310 --> 31:40.770
don't mean anything to us.

31:44.480 --> 31:46.140
Of course, it's not just them.

31:47.030 --> 31:48.160
As far as I know,

31:49.590 --> 31:51.640
Qingshan Manor has planted spies

31:52.110 --> 31:53.840
in both Biantang and Great Yan.

31:53.880 --> 31:56.510
Although I have left Qingshan Manor
for a long time,

31:56.510 --> 31:57.830
with the abilities I had

31:57.830 --> 31:59.240
when I was still in charge of it,

31:59.240 --> 32:00.350
within 10 days,

32:00.720 --> 32:03.200
I can uproot all these hidden sentries.

32:03.880 --> 32:04.680
By then,

32:04.960 --> 32:07.220
your years of hard work in Qingshan Manor

32:07.750 --> 32:09.480
will go down the drain.

32:11.720 --> 32:12.330
Master!

32:21.030 --> 32:21.960
Yue,

32:22.480 --> 32:25.790
actually, before I came to Ximeng,

32:27.510 --> 32:29.400
I already expected

32:30.510 --> 32:32.350
the result would be like this.

32:33.720 --> 32:36.110
I raised you since you were little.

32:36.270 --> 32:37.640
I know you best.

32:39.640 --> 32:41.200
Once you make a decision,

32:43.640 --> 32:45.310
you won't change it easily.

32:46.270 --> 32:52.200
But I just didn't want to admit defeat.

32:53.000 --> 32:54.750
I wanted to try again

33:00.240 --> 33:00.830
to see

33:02.440 --> 33:04.030
if I could keep you.

33:04.750 --> 33:07.200
I can't force you to do anything,

33:07.200 --> 33:09.550
nor can I make any decisions for you.

33:10.200 --> 33:12.640
If Qingshan Manor

33:13.200 --> 33:14.440
is destined to end

33:14.440 --> 33:16.830
in my hands,

33:18.590 --> 33:20.160
that is destiny.

33:20.720 --> 33:22.960
I can only watch helplessly

33:23.590 --> 33:26.000
as the Muhe family gets what they want.

33:29.680 --> 33:30.590
I...

33:31.750 --> 33:34.720
have one last thing to remind you.

33:35.270 --> 33:37.240
If Qingshan Manor can find you,

33:38.030 --> 33:40.200
anyone in Great Yong can do the same.

33:40.960 --> 33:45.480
As many people
are watching our Zhuge family,

33:45.790 --> 33:48.920
just as many are watching you,

33:49.400 --> 33:51.000
including His Majesty

33:51.270 --> 33:52.110
and

33:52.350 --> 33:55.110
those who want to ascend the throne
of Great Yong in the future.

33:55.110 --> 33:55.880
If you...

33:57.000 --> 33:58.750
want to leave Qingshan Manor

33:59.070 --> 34:01.070
and live according to your own will,

34:01.400 --> 34:02.350
you can only...

34:05.590 --> 34:07.400
rely on yourself.

34:21.230 --> 34:22.440
Yue.

34:23.960 --> 34:24.960
I...

34:26.360 --> 34:28.920
am already in my twilight years.

34:29.110 --> 34:30.440
I can only...

34:32.030 --> 34:33.190
do this much for you.

34:34.190 --> 34:34.800
You...

34:36.110 --> 34:38.320
take care of yourself.

34:45.550 --> 34:46.440
Zhuge Yue,

34:47.000 --> 34:48.710
don't think that because you saved me,

34:48.710 --> 34:50.770
what you have done can be written off.

34:51.000 --> 34:52.150
One day,

34:52.480 --> 34:54.679
I will eventually kill you for revenge.

35:07.440 --> 35:09.480
This Xiaoba is really ungrateful.

35:09.710 --> 35:11.440
And I even gave her a good horse.

36:13.030 --> 36:16.880
Congratulations to the King and Queen
of Ximeng on implementing the new policy.

36:16.880 --> 36:17.800
This seems

36:18.030 --> 36:19.420
to be some kind of sacrifice.

36:19.420 --> 36:21.860
Let Great Yong and Great Yan fight again!

36:22.110 --> 36:23.510
Let him kill Zhao Che!

36:23.800 --> 36:24.840
Everyone infected with the plague

36:24.840 --> 36:26.070
ends up with their entire body rotting.

36:26.070 --> 36:27.030
What's wrong with you?

36:27.030 --> 36:28.550
Chu, you belong to me,

36:29.400 --> 36:30.710
me alone.

36:31.280 --> 36:32.360
I never thought

36:32.710 --> 36:34.110
I would have a day like this with you.
